thread.title: BRIEF-Woolworth Cyprus To Issue 45,1 Mln Shares Resulting From Distribution Of A Dividend In The Form Of Shares

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Woolworth Cyprus To Issue 45,1 Mln Shares Resulting From Distribution Of A Dividend In The Form Of Shares
text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - WOOLWORTH CYPRUS PROPERTIES :
* TO ISSUE 45.1 MLN SHARES RESULTING FROM DISTRIBUTION OF A DIVIDEND IN THE FORM OF SHARES
* SHARES WILL BE INCORPORATED INTO THE ALREADY LISTED SHARE CAPITAL OF THE COMPANY, WHICH WILL AMOUNT TO 214.0 MLN SHARES.
Source text : bit.ly/2nTmcyI
